wikimedia-globalblocking-ipblocked:
'''Ethoonyeryo-anyu IP yaari [[m:Special:MyLanguage/Global blocks|yoottipihiwa mwa n"wiki mootheene]].'''

Ottipihiwa wenno ovariwe ni $1 ($2).
Mwaha wooniheriwe waari ''$3''.

* Opaceriwa ottipihiwa: $4
* Omalamala wa okathi woottipihiwa: $5

Ethoonyeryo-anyu IP ya naanano ti $6.
Mukhalihe muhina sotheene seiya sa osulu ni mmuhupini munkelaanyu oniveleeliherya, xontte. 

Mwaakupaliki wira muttipihiwe mwaha woowattattanyiwa, mookhala oophwanyaka ihaali ikina ni ittharihelo omweettiheryoni wa sotheene sooluluwana ni [[m:Special:MyLanguage/No open proxies|okhoottihiwa wa "proxies" soohuliwa]].
Wahikhale siiso, woowi nvaanyihane ottipihiwa wenno [[m:Steward requests/Global|muthukule nivekelo nimosa woowi yooniwe ni Meta-Wiki]].
